data.description: This beautifully renovated 6 Bed/3 Bath, Brick Bungalow in the Montclare/Galewood neighborhood is priced to sell! Features include a new white gourmet kitchen with quartz counters and stainless steel appliances, 3 beautifully renovated bathrooms, one on each level. HVAC & water heater new in 2022. New fence and 2 car garage with party door. Newer Roof. Sunroom off the kitchen that opens up to a beautiful, new wood deck and backyard. House is in great condition but being sold AS IS.
